-- BCE shares jump after court backs buyout
-- 
-- Fri Jun 20, 2008 5:01pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/06/20/us-markets-stocks-bce-idUSN2034803320080620

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Shares of BCE Inc, Canada's largest telecom company, rose 8.8 percent to $37.10 in extended trade on Friday after it won the backing of the Supreme Court of Canada to proceed with the world's biggest leveraged buyout. 

